    "guide": "<h3>🏖️ Best Beaches: At a Glance</h3><table class='beach-table'><thead><tr><th>Beach</th><th>Rating</th><th>Type</th><th>Facilities</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Skala Eressos</strong></td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</td><td>Grey Sand</td><td>Bohemian Hub</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Vatera</strong></td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</td><td>Sand</td><td>Extensive</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Agios Isidoros</strong></td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</td><td>Pebble</td><td>Organized</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Tarti</strong></td><td>⭐⭐⭐⭐</td><td>Gold Sand</td><td>Tavernas</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>📅 5-Day Driving Itinerary</h3><div class='itinerary-step'><strong>Day 1: Arrival (~10km).</strong> Collect car at the airport and head to Mytilene city.</div><div class='itinerary-step'><strong>Day 2: The North (~65km).</strong> Drive to the medieval village of Molyvos.</div><div class='itinerary-step'><strong>Day 3: The West (~70km).</strong> Visit the Petrified Forest and stay in the bohemian Skala Eressos.</div><div class='itinerary-step'><strong>Day 4: Wetlands (45km).</strong> Explore the Kalloni salt flats and birdwatching spots.</div><div class='itinerary-step'><strong>Day 5: The South & Departure (~120km).</strong> Visit Plomari, then drive back to the airport.</div>"
